CHECK_ACTIVEID Eindride
BEQ 10 s0 sC
	MUSC FE11_Preparations
	TEXTSTART
	TEXTSHOW HartnerSparedByEindrideText
	TEXTEND
	MUSC FE11_TogetherWeRide
	TEXTCONT
	TEXTEND
	REMA
	ENUT 22
	GOTO 8
